if I could give a ZERO star, I would!!!!!!
Une agence à éviter, j'ai ouvert mon compte chez eux il y a quelque années, et je regrette ce choix vivement !!!! la cerise sur le gâteau est le personnel nuulll du personnel, j'ai eu beaucoup de problèmes avec eux et n'ont jamais essayé de les résoudre, finalement je suis allé voir le directeur de l'agence, celui là m'a traité comme une ***, il était impoli, m'a interrompu pendant que je parlais, n'a même pas essayé de comprendre le problème. Ils vous donneront tous n'importe quelle excuse et vous demanderont de chercher une solution ailleurs juste pour se débarrasser de vous.
Personne ne vous répondra au téléphone, personne ne rependra à vos emails...
Scandaleux! Je vous déconseille. faites vos recherche avant de les rejoindre.
column340:
if I could give a ZERO star, I would!!!!!!
An agency to avoid, I opened my account with them a few years ago, and I deeply regret this choice!!!! the icing on the cake is the staff nuulll staff, i had many problems with them and never tried to solve them, finally i went to the agency manager, that one treated me like a***, he was rude, interrupted me while I was talking, didn't even try to understand the issue. They will all give you any excuse and ask you to look for a solution elsewhere just to get rid of you.
No one will answer your phone, no one will answer your emails...
Scandalous! I do not advise you. do your research before joining them.

On me fait patienter au téléphone pendant plus d'une heure sans régler le problème. JE NE RECOMMANDE PAS LA BANQUE CIH

Really to avoid even fleeing.

- Je suis client de cette banque depuis 10 ans, et depuis l'arrivée du nouveau directeur de banque, il a causé toute cette corruption, et la relation avec les clients est devenue très mauvaise. Cela s'est produit plusieurs fois.

+ الابناك كاتسد 15:45 و كايسربيو الناس لي جاو في الوقت ... هادو كايحبسو مع 15:00  بدعوى راه خاص نساليو بكري كانبقا هنا مورا 16:00 !؟

column340:
The best banking agency in town...
System toujours en panne,
And the application does not work..You cannot take out your money or transfer it, you cannot transfer it through the application...even the quiche is once served and once standing...
Waiting time is an hour after two hours
hustle
There is only one quiche in the master, except when I go to lunch, the service stops and the customers are left in the sun for two hours.
And of course, friends and acquaintances would come out to them until they brought them in.
+ The sons were arrested at 15:45, and the people who came to prison at the time... They were imprisoned at 15:00, on the pretext of a private opinion, and we asked Bakri to stay here at 16:00!?
- And, of course, the security guard, as usual in Morocco, has more authority than the manager... He manages everything conseil, action commerciale, traitement des réclamations, and this is a favor from him, of course, and thanks for him.
+ I do not advise anyone to deal with this agency... At least the rest of the agencies are better in terms of management and waiting time... And the general problem remains that CIH is already deficient in terms of quality of services... It remains in advertisements and marketing..
